properties.name: Orders
properties.comments:
A Product can be marked as Favorite by several Customers, but this denormalized modeling approach does not clearly represent that.

In this case, the cardinality should be n-n instead of n-1 in the derivation, but Hackolade Studio cannot identify this.

properties.name: Catalog
properties.comments:
An Account Manager has several suppliers, but this denormalized modeling approach does not clearly represent that.

In this case, the cardinality should be n-1 instead of 1-1 in the derivation, but Hackolade Studio cannot identify this.
